# Sprint Relay Debug Verification Checklist

- [x] Navigate to http://localhost:3000/
- [x] Wait for initial tasks to load
- [x] Find sprint selection dropdown at the top right area
- [x] Select "Sprint 7"
- [x] Wait for dashboard to stabilize
- [x] Confirm >0 tasks for Sprint 7 remain visible

## Findings
- Successfully navigated to http://localhost:3000/.
- Initial load showed Sprint 7 with 67 tasks.
- Switched to Sprint 8 (showed 0 tasks) and then back to Sprint 7.
- After switching back to Sprint 7, it briefly showed "Loading Sprint Telemetry..." and "Total Tasks 0", then correctly loaded and displayed **67 tasks**.
- Tasks remained visible and stable for over 10 seconds.
- No "flashing and disappearing" behavior was observed for Sprint 7.
